{"tid":632366,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣桌遊出版商在台參展  因受到中國出版商威嚇  最終要退出展覽","createTime":"2018-04-17T10:11:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-19T09:46:07.000Z","uid":46430,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"484ec41d421bd2cf5faf9f978319d369c5f3198b","tid":632366,"uid":46430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T10:11:56.000Z","msg":"事源係台灣出版社美麗島風雲出左隻新GAME叫做《誰是強國人》，以下節錄自佢地既作品描述： <br />\n<br />\n「在本作中，玩家將分別扮演台灣、港澳、西藏、新疆、日韓等國家的最高決策者，決策目標很簡單，在強國人大舉入侵我們領土的時刻，我們要選擇高舉抗爭到底的旗幟、還是咬牙跪拜以換取不流血的偏安一隅？」<br />\n<br />\n黎緊5月晌高雄有個叫「月光桌遊節」，美麗島風雲都會去參展，但最近就因為《誰是強國人》呢隻GAME引起左另一間來自中國既參展商戰鼓社不滿，仲話要拉隊連同全中國參展商一同退展以示抗議，最終美麗島風雲為左平息事件，宣佈退展。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/TheWonderfulIsLand/photos/a.153882474761056.35455.138583586290945/1006588056157156/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FTheWonderfulIsLand%2Fphotos%2Fa.153882474761056.35455.138583586290945%2F1006588056157156%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=nwxsaOv4DVDwxxgDlY5mHYM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=e64c12b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/TheWonderfulIsLand/photos/a.153882474761056.35455.138583586290945/1006588056157156/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n至於展覽主辦方又點講？「確認兩方退出的內容後，我們心中是千百的無奈與遺憾。但我們必須重申「月光桌遊節不存在任何政治立場或偏頗。」然後，就沒然後......<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/BGFes.TW/posts/2319085611651585\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FBGFes.TW%2Fposts%2F2319085611651585&d=nwxsaOv4DVDwxxgDlY5mHYM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=4234400f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/BGFes.TW/posts/2319085611651585</a><br />\n<br />\nD大陸人真係痴Q線，周圍亂吠！<br />\n睇到火都黎埋  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4208df37446ce4324409dff6ac7c442a6d8b3b1c","tid":632366,"uid":6777,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy"